<section id="assisted" class="section section--cream">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="intro-split">
      <div class="intro-split__body reveal">
        <span class="eyebrow">Assisted Living</span>
        <h2>Personalized support, delivered with warmth.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Care plans are built around each resident &mdash; never the other way around. We coordinate with physicians and family to provide exactly the level of assistance needed, and nothing more.</p>
        <p>As one of only two licensed assisted living providers in Fayette County, we hold ourselves to a higher regulatory standard than personal care homes. Our on-site licensed nurses, 24/7 staffing, and 16-hour nursing coverage means help is always close at hand. See <a href="/about/">our approach to licensed senior care</a> for more.</p>
        <ul class="tag-list">
          <li>Individualized care plans</li>
          <li>Medication reminders &amp; administration</li>
          <li>Bathing &amp; dressing assistance</li>
          <li>Transfer &amp; mobility support</li>
          <li>Blood pressure monitoring</li>
          <li>24-hour call system with pendant</li>
          <li>On-site licensed RN &amp; LPN</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="intro-split__media reveal">
        <img src="{{ images.communityExterior }}" alt="Residential exterior with landscaped grounds" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

