        <h2>A short stay. A real rest.</h2>
        <p class="lead">Recovering from surgery? Caregiver needs a vacation? Testing the waters before committing to a longer stay? Respite care offers a fully furnished suite and every community amenity for a week, a month, or anything in between.</p>
        <p>Respite residents enjoy all the dining, wellness, activities, and <a href="/amenities/">care services of long-term residents</a> &mdash; without a long-term commitment.</p>
